pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: sol-image
    elementType: image
    bounds: [0, 0, 560, 720]
    src: "/mnt/agents/output/war-room-deck/images/chess_strategy.png"
    fit: {mode: cover}

  - elementId: sol-fade
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [400, 0, 200, 720]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: gradient
      gradientType: linear
      angle: 0
      stops:
        - {position: 0, color: "#0F171200"}
        - {position: 1, color: "#0F1712"}

  - elementId: sol-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [600, 120, 600, 24]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>THE SOLUTION</p>

  - elementId: sol-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [600, 160, 600, 140]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      fontSize: 36
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Model the players. Test your move. See the counter.</p>

  - elementId: sol-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [600, 320, 580, 300]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 20
      lineHeight: 1.7
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>The War Room is a browser-based stakeholder simulator.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px">Build dossiers on the people around your idea — their personality traits, political stance, and payoff structure. Then test any move against them.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px">The engine plays each stakeholder <span style="color:$primary;">in character</span> — showing their private read, likely objections, and your best counter.</p>

  - elementId: sol-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [600, 680, 600, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$primary"}

  - elementId: sol-brand
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1020, 688, 180, 22]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      fontSize: 11
      letterSpacing: 2
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>THE WAR ROOM</p>